        <akn:num>50-2301.04</akn:num>
        <akn:heading>Hearing examiners.</akn:heading>
<akn:subsection eId="subsec_50-2301_04_a">
      <akn:num>(a)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>The Director shall appoint and prescribe the duties of a Chief Hearing Examiner and other hearing examiners as are necessary to implement the provisions of this chapter. The Chief Hearing Examiner and each hearing examiner appointed pursuant to this section shall serve as career service employees in accordance with ยง 1-608.01.</akn:p></akn:content>
